<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Email Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

  <p>Please confirm your email address by using the code below or clicking the link.</p>

  <p><strong>Confirmation Code: {{emailVerificationCode}}</strong></p>

  <p>Or click here to verify: <a href="{{emailVerificationUrl}}">{{emailVerificationUrl}}</a></p>

  <p>This code expires in 24 hours. If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>

  <p>Thank you,</p>
  <p>Inventors Team</p>
</body>
</html>
